# {{context||New England|idiomatic|archaic|lang=en}} A generic [[greeting]] said to someone in the [[morning]].

====Usage notes====
This term should be considered [[archetypal]] or [[stereotypical]] of Irish speech, but is in truth a Hollywood invention.  It is never heard in Ireland. See [[Hollywood Irish]].

